  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Posting the Variation Margin</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loioba15da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Posting the Variation Margin </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You use this transaction to post the variation margin (key date margin) on each trading day. By doing this, the system can value all open positions with the variation margin at the settlement rate on a daily basis.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">On the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP Easy Access</span> screen, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Manager</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Derivatives</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Margin Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Post Variation Margin</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> .\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the security ID number, company code, and the key date.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> If you do not want the system to post close margin flows from the selected positions that have not yet been posted, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Post Close Margin</span> indicator. This ensures that only the flows on or before the key date are taken into account.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> To carry out a test run, without changing the data in the database, set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Test Run</span> indicator.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span> .\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}